Package: ezlimma
Type: Package
Title: Streamlines and extends limma package
Version: 0.2.2.9003
Authors@R: c(person("Jonathan", "Dreyfuss", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jdreyf@bu.edu"),
             person("Hui", "Pan", role = "aut"),
			 person("Grace", "Daher", role = "ctb"))
BugReports: https://github.com/jdreyf/ezlimma/issues
Description: Functions for more easily using limma, such as to test multiple 
    contrasts for genes or pathways in one line. Also, an Excel front-end for
	limma's pathway analysis functions roast and fry, and mediation analysis.
Imports:
	knitr,
	limma (>= 3.34.8),
	statmod,
	stats
